CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13 reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of woman wearing dark strapless satin dress with rose corsage and light colored shawl, posed in interior with flower and leaf patterned carpeting for Thirtieth Anniversary Convention of Girl Friends, Inc.
